title: Parkland's Siena Salvaggio is lehighvalleylive Girls Volleyball Player of the Week
text:
Siena Salvaggio , Parkland 
The senior opposite hitter was her usual stellar self as the Trojans experienced their typical success during the league tournament. 
Salvaggio, a PIAA champion in swimming, totaled 46 kills as Parkland defeated Freedom, Central Catholic and Liberty to win the Eastern Pennsylvania Conference championship, its sixth straight league title. 
She also had 23 digs and eight assists over the three matches. 
Honorable mention : Sr. MH Erika Foose , Parkland; Sr. S Kristin Krause , Parkland; Sr. MH Bre McDonald , Nazareth; Sr. MH Nioami Miranda , Hackettstown; So. MH Grace Mittl , Liberty; Jr. OH Dana Roberts , Central Catholic; Jr. OH Sydney Wilson , Liberty.
